file = {:Users/arnofoerster/Documents/Mendeley Desktop/Jiang, Engel/Journal of Chemical Physics/Jiang, Engel{\_}2005{\_}Second-order Kohn-Sham perturbation theory Correlation potential for atoms in a cavity.pdf:pdf},
